        {
          "why": "Features a highly refined, almost entirely achromatic UI where typography and crisp lines define components, and color is used sparingly for functional accents (though Linear uses a distinct accent color, Moffitt.Moffitt. explicitly does not).",
          "business": "Linear"
        }
